aac32e609300fecfaa242ec8e73af288a2fb9a7","tid":373753,"uid":32380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T09:11:01.000Z","msg":"有 但總係覺得佢鐘意我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae06531e864ef5e3787d583609c5d903f0c621ef","tid":373753,"uid":62755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T09:15:22.000Z","msg":"次次我唔開心都陪我傾<br />\n幾乎咩時間揾佢都秒回<br />\n但已經幾年冇見<br />\n一路雙方都會傾自己拍拖嘅野<br />\n點知最近同我講一路對我有野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}